U||   "Hush, fool!" snorted Hartkopf. "One word of that to the ear of Roger
U||   and you too are left behind. Of such non-essentials the Universe is
U||   full, to be collected in times of ease, but in times hard to be
U||   disregarded. Und this is a time of schrecklichkeit indeed!"
U||   And through that terrific conduit came speeding package after package
